                <a href="/blog/190433-A/coronavirus-update-hibernating-rhinos-is-offering-2-months-of-free-ravendb-support">
                        <h2>Coronavirus update: Hibernating Rhinos is offering 2 months of FREE RavenDB support</h2>
                </a>
            </div>
			
			<div class="timetoread">

				<div>
					<span class="icomoon-position icon-time" aria-hidden="true"></span>
					<span class="collapse"> time to read</span> <strong>2 min</strong> <span class="collapse">| <strong>303 words</strong></span>
